The `addressSupplier` method in `reactor.netty.tcp.TcpClient` `client` has been **deprecated** now. Use `remoteAddress(Supplier&lt;? extends SocketAddress&gt; remoteAddressSupplier)` instead.

Modifying the above code.
```
private ReactorNettyTcpClient&lt;byte[]&gt; createTcpClient() {
        ReactorNettyTcpClient unSecured;

        unSecured = new ReactorNettyTcpClient&lt;&gt;(
                client -&gt; client.remoteAddress(() -&gt; getAddress()).secure(),
                new StompReactorNettyCodec());

        return unSecured;
    }
