However, it will not work in the following scenario, unless you override the [equals](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/Object.html#equals-java.lang.Object-) method for SchoolObj:
```Java
List&lt;SchoolObj&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();
listOne.add(new SchoolObj(&quot;nameC&quot;, &quot;schoolD&quot;));
